	    <h2><a href="/news/">Library News</a></h2>
	    <div class='newsitem clearfix'>  
	        <div class='news_info'>  
   	        <div class='news_img'><a href="/news/details/vpl_adopts_access_without_fear_policy"><img src="/images/uploads/image/news/75x75_favicon.PNG" width="75" height="75" /></a></div>	        <p><a href="/news/details/vpl_adopts_access_without_fear_policy">VPL adopts ‘access without fear’ policy</a>
	        <br /><i>posted on May 05, 2016</i></p>
	        <p>Vancouver&rsquo;s library has adopted a new policy that echoes the City of Vancouver&rsquo;s commitment to provide access to city services without fear. <a href="http://www.vpl.ca/news/details/vpl_adopts_access_without_fear_policy" target="_self">Read more</a></p>	        </div><!-- news_info -->
	    </div><!-- newsitem -->
	    <div class='newsitem clearfix'>  
	        <div class='news_info'>  
   	        <div class='news_img'><a href="/news/details/central_library_expansion_showcase_-_may_2016"><img src="/images/uploads/image/news/Levels_8_9_New_Model_2016_75x75.jpg" width="75" height="71" /></a></div>	        <p><a href="/news/details/central_library_expansion_showcase_-_may_2016">VPL showcasing its plans to expand the central library </a>
	        <br /><i>posted on May 05, 2016</i></p>
	        <p>New floor plans, architectural renderings and models of the upcoming renovations now on display in the Level 7 foyer of the central library.</p>	        </div><!-- news_info -->
	    </div><!-- newsitem -->
	    <div class='newsitem clearfix'>  
	        <div class='news_info'>  
   	        <div class='news_img'><a href="https://vpl.bibliocommons.com/events/search/q=storyteller%20in%20residence"><img src="/images/uploads/image/news/ASIR2016_RenaeMorriseau_75x75.jpg" width="75" height="75" /></a></div>
   	        	        <p><a href="https://vpl.bibliocommons.com/events/search/q=storyteller%20in%20residence">Aboriginal Storyteller in Residence: May Events</a>
	        <br /><i>posted on April 26, 2016</i></p>
	        <p>Explore and celebrate storytelling and singing as a powerful force in our lives and our communities with VPL Storyteller in Residence, <a href="http://www.vpl.ca/programs/details/aboriginal_storyteller_2016"><strong>Renae Morriseau</strong></a>.</p>	        </div><!-- news_info -->
	    </div><!-- newsitem -->
	    <div class='newsitem clearfix'>  
	        <div class='news_info'>  
   	        <div class='news_img'><a href="https://vpl.bibliocommons.com/events/search/q=Expo%20Memory"><img src="/images/uploads/image/news/Expo86image_75x75.jpg" width="75" height="75" /></a></div>
   	        	        <p><a href="https://vpl.bibliocommons.com/events/search/q=Expo%20Memory">Expo Minute: Share your Expo 86 memory at VPL</a>
	        <br /><i>posted on April 26, 2016</i></p>
	        <p>Expo turns 30! <a href="https://vpl.bibliocommons.com/events/search/q=Expo%20Memory">Drop in</a> to the Inspiration Lab to record a brief audio clip about your favourite Expo 86 memory or <a href="http://www.vpl.ca/programs/details/expo">submit a photo</a> to VPL's Expo exhibition.</p>	        </div><!-- news_info -->
	    </div><!-- newsitem -->
	 
	         
